==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-iːm|-iːm]]

===Transitive verb===
'''to redeem''' ([[redeems]], [[redeemed]], [[redeeming]])
#To [[recover]] [[ownership]] of something by [[paying]] a sum
#To set free, [[rescue]] or [[ransom]]
#To save from a [[state]] of [[sin]] (and from its [[consequence]]s)
#To [[restore]] the [[reputation]] or [[honour]] of oneself or something

====Derived terms====
*[[redeemer]]
*[[redemption]]

